-- Mobi Doctor - Telemedicine Service (Madrid/Spain)
('Mobi Doctor', 'Telemedicine', 'Online telemedicine platform providing video and phone consultations with English-speaking doctors across Spain. Connect with licensed EU doctors in minutes from anywhere - no waiting rooms, no travel required. Services include urgent care consultations, medical prescriptions with English instructions, sick notes, and specialist referrals. Consultations available daily from 8am to 9pm. Accessible via smartphone (iOS and Android), tablet, or desktop. Ideal for expats, tourists, and international residents seeking convenient English-speaking medical care. Prescriptions are valid at local Spanish pharmacies and accepted by international insurance providers including AXA and Cigna.', 'Online Service (Serves all of Spain)', 'Madrid', 'Madrid', NULL, 'help@mobidoctor.eu', 'https://www.mobidoctor.eu', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
